import { Component,OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { FormsModule } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-employeeform', templateUrl: './employeeform.component.html', styleUrls: ['./employeeform.component.css'] }) export class EmployeeformComponent implements On { }formData = { name: '', designation: null, location: null, salary: '' }; submitForm(form: any) { if (form.valid) { // Form is valid, perform submission logic console.log(this.formData); // Example: Log form data } else { // Form is invalid, display error or handle accordingly } } }

Employee Form

Name is required.
Designation is required.
Location is required.
Salary is required.
